<h1>Video & Catalog Links</h1>
&nbsp;Focus on Global Insights Interview

<iframe allowfullscreen='' frameborder='0' height='169' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ck-o1uTBXA4' width='320'></iframe>
<p style='margin-left:3px;'>
In 2015 FocusOn Mining, Aggregates and Construction, Publisher / Editor-in-Chief, Rick Vanderkieft posed a number of industry and company related questions to Bob Kleason, Exec. Vice President of Unified® Screening and Crushing. Bob spoke about the current state of the industry and the new Unified management philosophy.
</p>
<p style='margin-left:3px;'>
It’s been a while since the first FOA interview with Bob and since then, the industry has faced some tough challenges. Bob told us that the company was poised to handle the future market demands and changes. What leadership position has Unified perfected to satisfy customers and to increase their market share.
</p>
<p style='margin-left:3px;'>
Robert Rue, on behalf of FocusOn, visited the Unified® Phoenix facility in Gilbert, AZ to meet with the COO Andrew Lentsch.
</p>
<p style='margin-left:3px;'>
<strong>
Watch the video (above) and listen to this brief discussion between Robert and Andrew.
</strong>
</p>
